<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>github Demo</title>
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <h1>Iframe Video Display</h1>
        <p>Below is an example of an iframe embedding a YouTube video:</p>
        <section>
        <h2>Example Iframe</h2>
        <p>This iframe embeds a YouTube video about the history of the internet:</p>
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/I0_951_MPE0" width="300" height="315" title="Example Iframe"
            allow="accelerometer autoplay clipboard-write encrypted-media gyroscope web-share"
            referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Another Example</h2>
            <p>Here is another iframe embedding a different YouTube video:</p>
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ" width="300" height="315" title="Another Example Iframe"
                allow="accelerometer autoplay clipboard-write encrypted-media gyroscope web-share"
                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Elchapo</h2>
            <p>Here is an iframe embedding a video about Elchapo:</p>
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3GwjfUFyY6M" width="300" height="315" title="Elchapo Iframe"
                allow="accelerometer autoplay clipboard-write encrypted-media gyroscope web-share"
                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen>
           
            </iframe>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>